{"id":"b4669236c88b1dd5fc7ceabdfb0e97f5cb6004e237a6e78b76a95a3bd0181739","item_id":"6b5d66625e:0","text":"当你想快速、轻松地设置外景照明，或者需要一些 look development（外观开发）时间，但手头没有 HDRI 可用于"}
{"id":"1212e2ab64a08ec5ced8175eb4e0b702d7cfc550ede4593bd2ead1444ee69a02","item_id":"6b5d66625e:1","text":"PxrDomeLight"}
{"id":"f2341cc8bde00956fede3a2b87973fe126fba4c3f662ce23f2ece3f058ac25ba","item_id":"6b5d66625e:2","text":"时，daylight simulation（日光模拟）非常有用。它的简单性和真实感让这种灯光成为艺术家的常用选择。"}
{"id":"e3dfbb0fa300f8c684a1c92c174d573610e8ba9431fcb0e79ed535ac7fac4dac","item_id":"6b5d66625e:3","text":"这是一种环境光，在晴朗或有霾的天空下使用简单的物理模型来模拟地表日光。天空模型基于"}
{"id":"503ecf7f24aebcb938bb2f32aaadf497a9000202d002c800a8580ecf2a9ac0de","item_id":"6b5d66625e:4","text":"日光实用解析模型"}
{"id":"0d2649bee0fc69e7d0da02071dec1068ed8c3f581996605b41df20fe256c891c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:5","text":"一文，作者为 A.J. Preetham、Peter Shirley 和 Brian Smits。太阳圆盘模型改编自 H.C. Hottel 的"}
{"id":"11ee5787fb940ea5c406db4aadc29b417b0e4f99ad59cc0cef28b274b373f0ca","item_id":"6b5d66625e:6","text":"估算晴朗大气中直射太阳辐射透射率的简单模型"}
{"id":"5da9d61bdadcb5d49fa654c9b1a3ba8e694f407b3fb656fd20d612b7f489392e","item_id":"6b5d66625e:7","text":"，并根据物理数据对浑浊度参数进行曲线拟合，同时使用简单的临边昏暗模型。"}
{"id":"349c139217b301ea29970f5873df95bfebd3a19e741e19f638222eb25d3c9d4d","item_id":"6b5d66625e:8","text":"你会看到对 \"non-physical\"（非物理）控制的提及。这些控制用于帮助艺术家忽略我们通常模拟的一些物理定律，从而制作由艺术指导的图像。"}
{"id":"e68b36b17cbd990802f57741cb75cf3a73fa66a61999b0cd70e3cf7d26cfb25f","item_id":"6b5d66625e:9","text":"Parameters（参数）"}
{"id":"a6d01dcff3bfd333edf90a50daac2104cefab98b85bdbba67c8209ab75eb6447","item_id":"6b5d66625e:10","text":"Intensity（强度）"}
{"id":"c8071dac8653202f1771825450d6a194c7b7349bd533fb752a3db140f2a303e4","item_id":"6b5d66625e:11","text":"线性缩放此灯光的贡献。"}
{"id":"cc5454a4b7ce211370dcd2aa0ae58d6b564eee7940b42de516d05f5b269c414b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:12","text":"Exposure（曝光）"}
{"id":"8ad2c788464ce7f437497e00db6e22b4b5903704c8f8d8ffde1f0326eb7fc617","item_id":"6b5d66625e:13","text":"以 2 的幂指定 area light（区域光）的曝光。曝光增加 1 会使光源发出的能量翻倍。值 0 会在光源处产生 1 的强度，-1 会产生 0.5。你可能会疑惑为什么要使用"}
{"id":"cc5454a4b7ce211370dcd2aa0ae58d6b564eee7940b42de516d05f5b269c414b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:14","text":"Exposure（曝光）"}
{"id":"e518cf95972d4837a0f0fe09f7af2251125f8848cfaf36e015d5231f3d354171","item_id":"6b5d66625e:15","text":"，答案是现实世界照明能量很高，典型曝光值较低；而若使用等效的"}
{"id":"a6d01dcff3bfd333edf90a50daac2104cefab98b85bdbba67c8209ab75eb6447","item_id":"6b5d66625e:16","text":"Intensity（强度）"}
{"id":"d3fc1379aa307c64f747e9157964259c97eea5ffb723bb43921ed2678c46d999","item_id":"6b5d66625e:17","text":"，则可能必须输入非常大的数值。熟悉摄影测量的艺术家也会觉得这种方式更顺手。"}
{"id":"9c8a9579abe55bdc8a7b97031705e2738d912de38a35262863d8f47e05d3d641","item_id":"6b5d66625e:18","text":"Direction（方向）"}
{"id":"b344d80e24a3679999fa964450b34bc24d1578a35509f934c1418b0a20d21a67","item_id":"6b5d66625e:19","text":"太阳的"}
{"id":"0794afd1bc3cdba652103ff3e3b7c00069aefd2212d1807872aa9df7fdff5fe4","item_id":"6b5d66625e:20","text":"apparent（表观）"}
{"id":"6a1b72ff45858a9e2a0e80aba56941c45794517c51d647f7b3d1a506d68a465c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:21","text":"方向，指向太阳中心。天顶位于 +Y（用于正午光照），地平线位于 XZ 平面（用于日出/日落）。注意，Y 分量必须为非负值。如果给出了月份，则忽略此项。在某些 DCC 应用中，例如 Maya，你可以在视口中使用操纵器手动更改 Sun direction（太阳方向）（在视口中选中 Daylight 图标后按 't'）。"}
{"id":"2e010caed2aa8705dc9d3e38aaa92acfd4c4999ac73ee460ac8229520947e393","item_id":"6b5d66625e:22","text":"Haziness（雾霾度）"}
{"id":"bdabc28f66c23e774f5843cf077b5717905443bcb62e4336836b514d445ca23b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:23","text":"天空的 turbidity（浑浊度）。模型下限为 1.7，表示异常清澈的天空；上限为 10，表示逆温状态。"}
{"id":"35477d7a5c4866b346005afe7508aa2dd4131e0fda4010f84824880815d76f74","item_id":"6b5d66625e:24","text":"Sky Tint（天空色调）"}
{"id":"6f5f2dde64ac22105686c8ce92da7a277bdcdec6d644413dc452c2b4922623c2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:25","text":"调整天空的贡献和颜色。默认的白色会给出基于实测物理值的结果。你也许可以用这种方式创建一些有趣的外星天空。将其设置为黑色会移除第一张图中显示的天空贡献。"}
{"id":"fa6c7d58a3623552ba03049090d879e6774d4e14840ae0409a8362b6901ed44c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:26","text":"Sun Tint（太阳色调）"}
{"id":"8eff95853d3f51749976cff2541d4f1a388a346792b72177002ea099f2aae8c5","item_id":"6b5d66625e:27","text":"调整太阳的贡献和颜色。默认的白色会给出基于实测物理值的结果。将其设置为黑色会像第一张图那样移除太阳贡献（如果你想创建自己的太阳贡献，可以这样做）。"}
{"id":"1a40c3b58c7fba76659f17e7c984e771e3ddb2b3b4810204b6006462e4d3852c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:28","text":"Sun Size（太阳尺寸）"}
{"id":"bec6ba3516f7d253e97516e511ce7129dbd92ad8e7be61c22f798ac9c755f311","item_id":"6b5d66625e:29","text":"缩放太阳在天空中的表观大小。保持为 1 可得到真实的太阳尺寸，即 0.55 度角直径。在 0.1 时，你几乎不会注意到太阳贡献已经降低。注意，在 80.0 时，天空中会出现非常大的太阳，并且由于灯光尺寸直径增大，会投射更柔和的 shadows（阴影）。"}
{"id":"d6d397f3c91d53285b287a378cbd35bd021fa59cd21578681954cd4a281f07a5","item_id":"6b5d66625e:30","text":"Ground Mode（地面模式）"}
{"id":"e0d673edbdd7a820712f424a161bbdc753ecad6760288733e70acca174ab6349","item_id":"6b5d66625e:31","text":"此菜单允许用户更改虚拟地平面的外观和效果。Legacy Mode（旧版模式）按以往方式运行。Horizon Clamping（地平线钳制）使用模糊地平线更好地模拟虚拟地面模式。Diffuse Ground（漫反射地面）允许用户为无限虚拟地平面着色。"}
{"id":"4951f62a73fdbde5e62aabd253e8410fbd111d139f7ab0a224e4e2166f5c870e","item_id":"6b5d66625e:32","text":"Ground Color（地面颜色）"}
{"id":"452790e9a98d1f6439b53c8d6f12218b59d3244ee2930aecebe37fb6ab4ad15b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:33","text":"使用此颜色作为渲染出的地面颜色。它不可贴图化，也不接收 shadows（阴影）。"}
{"id":"310ca503ef36f177ddbc760463fcaec1edc6eca12bfd590ad7bb244b31e59543","item_id":"6b5d66625e:34","text":"Month（月份）"}
{"id":"318360b3a6f2105855c8da4abca5db669488fe6d2ffa1b63425fbade00fca8a5","item_id":"6b5d66625e:35","text":"一年中的月份，范围为 1 到 12。默认值"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:36","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"e057504e9218257c5a2747d6bf6a2ed8fdad5e6641eecd554d399e37e2cd8d22","item_id":"6b5d66625e:37","text":"表示使用显式给定的太阳方向，而不是自动计算。"}
{"id":"8f2364e11b8be3ff008f32b3dedb54e659362429bcc9e3eb6acb6070de4ffbff","item_id":"6b5d66625e:38","text":"Day（日期）"}
{"id":"35c84c084b592b554caf1b41ca553a71b63da95da5dcf236828b58b672d91240","item_id":"6b5d66625e:39","text":"月份中的日期，范围为 1 到 31。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:40","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:41","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"89f6832560dec0b7f8721d1fe3ba0b5036a5d1464ce4339bb16c3e1485bfec34","item_id":"6b5d66625e:42","text":"Year（年份）"}
{"id":"77d7bacccbcca3dec0dd22d60a82169607485939c5b3751809fd32c249107c3f","item_id":"6b5d66625e:43","text":"四位数年份。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:44","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:45","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"f0063b808736318d3f5038c3a6c3b6349183cc678ed93d2e7963248ae7ed7318","item_id":"6b5d66625e:46","text":"Hour（小时）"}
{"id":"b512fe7f231a52e14256120acf3a50261b8fba91b0207a28b809425f48de5041","item_id":"6b5d66625e:47","text":"自当地标准时间午夜以来经过的小时数。可以使用小数来包含分钟和秒。如果正在使用夏令时，请减去 1 以校正为标准时间。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:48","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:49","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"a8a06e4a5695553c674ef4cf83caa357f4ea25167fe957b3761e7834c94f88cb","item_id":"6b5d66625e:50","text":"Zone（时区）"}
{"id":"90fbb8e64feeffe7a07005bd9ca9db3e4af5b47b5e11d955a2dec048b2bad53c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:51","text":"相对于 GMT/UTC 的标准时区偏移，单位为小时。东为正，西为负。例如，太平洋时间为 -8。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:52","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:53","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"238a676da45a2f9c02f338b42799e07d172632a17d8673f93dbfb7e2571a999b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:54","text":"Latitude（纬度）"}
{"id":"949fe269a2eda1bebc17669ce79bb877595feff650facac36140048ea4283e93","item_id":"6b5d66625e:55","text":"纬度，单位为度。北为正，南为负。范围为 -90 到 +90 度。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:56","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:57","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"6d80458fd17d33fcc40825346bbdf2a8deb4b53a825839c21bc0e2c2c9f401b8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:58","text":"Longitude（经度）"}
{"id":"3d16af8d7d85d5dfc45d7bd692ed2ad97f697c28845bc3fab8a9723e69436e5e","item_id":"6b5d66625e:59","text":"经度，单位为度。东为正，西为负。范围为 -180 到 180 度。如果 Month 设置为"}
{"id":"c15106931263ccb6a396ed72ca1eadbfdb51abc0559d3447375b021ccf4bc4ad","item_id":"6b5d66625e:60","text":"use direction（使用方向）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:61","text":"，则忽略此项。"}
{"id":"1e7f34ee8f771657a4c8350d8589f8b2405544de0e756fecb4247e307d673bfc","item_id":"6b5d66625e:62","text":"Refine（细化）"}
{"id":"e444834d64a4a3fd087a67df3468ccacca520875122124d0d195e8b8e006e101","item_id":"6b5d66625e:63","text":"Specular Amount（高光量）"}
{"id":"d83cc85309d08114d78716c869026178cde0ef20548238b10ec44864bf52c7f3","item_id":"6b5d66625e:64","text":"发出的 specular light（高光光照）数量。这是一个 non-physical（非物理）控制。你可以使用 Specular Amount 为 0.0 的灯光，让它只作为场景对象的 diffuse light（漫反射光照）来源，并避免添加高光。"}
{"id":"9afefd5c02c99d5aad7e8dd8c7adb15934039c880d30638d4d649768f1458856","item_id":"6b5d66625e:65","text":"Diffuse Amount（漫反射量）"}
{"id":"bfcf0f2a24a9d5a5b29106e6d12c420fc007d8995ccf5ef314a23e50d55d1298","item_id":"6b5d66625e:66","text":"发出的 diffuse light（漫反射光照）数量。这是一个 non-physical（非物理）控制。你可以使用 Diffuse Amount 为 0.0 的灯光，让它只作为场景对象的高光来源。"}
{"id":"2a19bdc09aa3bd9d5ba8c9707687136c2825da0e2af28b7c5de7c65b9c50f365","item_id":"6b5d66625e:67","text":"Shadows（阴影）"}
{"id":"79cb58ea842eb86c9ad17f66578de711f48b284b7f3717c8d239dae3b01d7fe3","item_id":"6b5d66625e:68","text":"如果灯光的"}
{"id":"f4d3a2f271156e6358087cfb3ac2512cab7e39689c1f0484ba02c936081ea73c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:69","text":"Trace Light Paths"}
{"id":"477f7e97f9193a091d9189a2ab2eca07029f86cc84af6f2ecf0c85eb12a7c875","item_id":"6b5d66625e:70","text":"在 Advanced 中启用，则所有阴影参数都会被忽略。以下选项在非默认状态下使用时都是 non-physical（非物理）控制。如果"}
{"id":"f4d3a2f271156e6358087cfb3ac2512cab7e39689c1f0484ba02c936081ea73c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:71","text":"Trace Light Paths"}
{"id":"a5dea72893d8099a518099616827b2ee00922d365ec453e3ce9fe81b9e5389b1","item_id":"6b5d66625e:72","text":"启用，则会强制执行它们的物理性质。"}
{"id":"d286f42dd9fa1ccbc4408c49f141f87e4482d8b88834c823666b496a66a05e46","item_id":"6b5d66625e:73","text":"Enable Shadows（启用阴影）"}
{"id":"e536e9b0ea833097a1a1654a8679b7794fa04e75262e2cf1278d3abc740965e3","item_id":"6b5d66625e:74","text":"启用 raytraced shadows（光线追踪阴影）。下方示例为开启（默认）和关闭。"}
{"id":"6946fd2382957f0655d0fd423e1699825089519d5bf4903df891d5d5f327a146","item_id":"6b5d66625e:75","text":"Shadow Color（阴影颜色）"}
{"id":"cd6e630e6b056fd62a298c391291f46e92bda33c1f789d385234b5076bd23253","item_id":"6b5d66625e:76","text":"由发射光投射出的 shadows（阴影）颜色。"}
{"id":"51bf2649416c6d8f0d023ce582f0d8d65b25d81bac519b57ae585a4770f276f2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:77","text":"Shadow Max Distance（阴影最大距离）"}
{"id":"950d1d4b188d46f308ef2ac49109bac86e732c3f0dfeb55c1ac3a0003a4f755d","item_id":"6b5d66625e:78","text":"从被着色点位置开始计算的阴影最大距离。-1.0 表示未设置，此时会使用被着色点与灯光上点之间的距离。你可以使用此控制人为缩短 shadows（阴影）的投射距离。这也可能通过不计算该距离之外的阴影来提高渲染速度。这里它用于移除阳光在后墙上的阴影。"}
{"id":"ca6a1f4bade57a14da1dc6abfd08b3ff6b65ad156ae60b4b116e99ce980a730d","item_id":"6b5d66625e:79","text":"Shadow Falloff（阴影衰减）"}
{"id":"ca0eb9bccfa7be61c168599559263b31f79a787e62cb41cff7e848383238214b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:80","text":"阴影衰减开始的距离，以灯光为起点。-1.0 会关闭阴影衰减。它与"}
{"id":"51bf2649416c6d8f0d023ce582f0d8d65b25d81bac519b57ae585a4770f276f2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:81","text":"Shadow Max Distance（阴影最大距离）"}
{"id":"e28cc17561cd003c60ef8d46dd6b7d64a1d0b094b144b3ca9219d5e4a86bf70a","item_id":"6b5d66625e:82","text":"一起使用，为 shadows（阴影）创建伪淡出，这些阴影会被"}
{"id":"51bf2649416c6d8f0d023ce582f0d8d65b25d81bac519b57ae585a4770f276f2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:83","text":"Shadow Max Distance（阴影最大距离）"}
{"id":"8f4e99ba2ac16934da439b3e39b6342a88659faf11a123f355b66b4b337f2cb7","item_id":"6b5d66625e:84","text":"参数缩短或截断。下方示例同时使用两个参数，并提高了衰减。注意，此参数可能影响复杂照明设置的性能。"}
{"id":"57e929e07ef635a298c2bdea244b008d2b7c1048e01880663cf7392370e61714","item_id":"6b5d66625e:85","text":"Shadow Falloff Gamma（阴影衰减 Gamma）"}
{"id":"097730120247b4ac333aa29a6c8d6dc5881dccb9279da77b3eaeeac0f2e7fea8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:86","text":"衰减区域中阴影强度的 gamma。这需要使用"}
{"id":"51bf2649416c6d8f0d023ce582f0d8d65b25d81bac519b57ae585a4770f276f2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:87","text":"Shadow Max Distance（阴影最大距离）"}
{"id":"6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0","item_id":"6b5d66625e:88","text":"和"}
{"id":"ca6a1f4bade57a14da1dc6abfd08b3ff6b65ad156ae60b4b116e99ce980a730d","item_id":"6b5d66625e:89","text":"Shadow Falloff（阴影衰减）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:90","text":"。"}
{"id":"1b26903730584e4c1b45d17deede65854378add523b666c14b8d58e0d2eafa33","item_id":"6b5d66625e:91","text":"Trace Subset（追踪子集）"}
{"id":"647df01b1c6a0736a6b250aaa35d5bbff7566d1fb4ef2e7bace7332f257b162c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:92","text":"用于 traced shadow intersection（追踪阴影相交）时考虑的几何体集合。如果未指定，则所有几何体都会被纳入追踪阴影相交计算。"}
{"id":"dba929755de1ed9625dcb118bd5b558eff41bc2969c84f8c9df370006fc396e6","item_id":"6b5d66625e:93","text":"Don't Trace Subset（不追踪子集）"}
{"id":"4c2bf7892e3dfa3eb429291a4e5b3ebced4b3d1d6e6e4ca2b6ff3cfb8ee084da","item_id":"6b5d66625e:94","text":"用于 traced shadow intersection（追踪阴影相交）时忽略的几何体集合。如果未指定，则所有几何体都会用于追踪阴影相交计算。"}
{"id":"9f088dbebd6c3c70a5ddbc2c943b11e4ca9acea5757b0b4f2b32479f0dbb747e","item_id":"6b5d66625e:95","text":"Advanced（高级）"}
{"id":"f4d3a2f271156e6358087cfb3ac2512cab7e39689c1f0484ba02c936081ea73c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:96","text":"Trace Light Paths"}
{"id":"0406ce3c1cb7758cf4edf7fd4b28e58f638ec7013738d0782780d6978e483c2b","item_id":"6b5d66625e:97","text":"启用来自此灯光的 light tracing（光线追踪）和 photon tracing（光子追踪）。此值会强制灯光遵循物理，并且副作用是禁用上面的"}
{"id":"2a19bdc09aa3bd9d5ba8c9707687136c2825da0e2af28b7c5de7c65b9c50f365","item_id":"6b5d66625e:98","text":"Shadows（阴影）"}
{"id":"884079fff297815e9e7fda095637d704ac451d53732df93aeaf55122004b79dc","item_id":"6b5d66625e:99","text":"控制。使用 PxrVCM 或 PxrUPBP Integrators 时，用户可以借此有选择地决定哪些灯光发射 photons（光子）。"}
{"id":"6a6a7b9ec714f50c6b9c5a6d79cfdc469364587ccecbb4d9775f6aa6efd715e6","item_id":"6b5d66625e:100","text":"Thin Shadow"}
{"id":"45416f017c5424b5054e29927bbe4741292994d5369a91373048cc4e76c0c5fb","item_id":"6b5d66625e:101","text":"为此灯光启用 thin shadow（薄阴影），并禁用 refraction caustics（折射焦散）。如果"}
{"id":"f4d3a2f271156e6358087cfb3ac2512cab7e39689c1f0484ba02c936081ea73c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:102","text":"Trace Light Paths"}
{"id":"d1d3e2f303a085bd3dbe07a9256180e90ce3d84c39131ecfca91dc0790e90404","item_id":"6b5d66625e:103","text":"启用，则会忽略此参数。这是一个 non-physical（非物理）控制，可以为透射对象创建 \"fake\" colored shadows（伪彩色阴影），而不需要为焦散生成 photons（光子）。下面从 On（默认）切换到 Off（不透明阴影）。注意，选择 Off 会失去彩色阴影和内部彩色反射，但会换来一些渲染速度。"}
{"id":"c188208684d330de3c17be7aeaa9a197f0fe2b06fbac588614338433600a91c2","item_id":"6b5d66625e:104","text":"Visible in Refraction（折射中可见）"}
{"id":"98dfa1059315327e15e4fe20ef13c2853e336f68b97296372587a0833ee19e80","item_id":"6b5d66625e:105","text":"开启后，使灯光可通过玻璃和窗户等 transmission effects（透射效果）被看见。"}
{"id":"75f6369479e4700694fe684f0e46559e7d1e8c2e9496265fc78f5b7cb9cacbec","item_id":"6b5d66625e:106","text":"Manifold Walk（流形行走）"}
{"id":"ecd5045216220c61cb868b83822ad154e584f74b93d052a2700d4cf27c1037fb","item_id":"6b5d66625e:107","text":"与 PxrUnified Integrator 一起使用，并启用"}
{"id":"d73bfbfa7ffb9e115d07c7f5c0945c2ace3bd843daaf76ce60d0d0020fee3ff0","item_id":"6b5d66625e:108","text":"Enable Manifold Walk（启用 Manifold Walk（流形行走））"}
{"id":"d87af900d5c9c430c33292b69b80a1cb9adc5046ac72c096de6e76ba3a78b025","item_id":"6b5d66625e:109","text":"以创建低成本焦散。注意：必须禁用 Thin Shadows"}
{"id":"a1aa44b0de90692049bb2f4fc1f23c3f2acb345ec594cbec80eaa1f706465ec8","item_id":"6b5d66625e:110","text":"Manifold Walk Exclude Group（Manifold Walk（流形行走）排除组）"}
{"id":"ecd5045216220c61cb868b83822ad154e584f74b93d052a2700d4cf27c1037fb","item_id":"6b5d66625e:111","text":"与 PxrUnified Integrator 一起使用，并启用"}
{"id":"c2a09ed674c8090996a6675ce8841dd8cfbc86b267d8dbb53b818a205366257b162c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:112","text":"Enable Manifold Walk（启用 Manifold Walk（流形行走）），"}
{"id":"22a155cf25c322aea3db6fdae517e0ccdfbbd9f25ea8a8fbd4fb1c4fbeb3a1d7","item_id":"6b5d66625e:113","text":"此 trace set（追踪集合）在 manifold exploration（流形探索）期间会被忽略，以避免停止或遮挡流形探索射线"}
{"id":"67ab01fa55d65ff19cf07dfb97d172285446c161a2453f80b7143b56d48e792a","item_id":"6b5d66625e:114","text":"Light Samples"}
{"id":"896caad6537544e98fedfbd8cc2e3dc4ac609ff239baf1532ca4c4be9481de5c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:115","text":"指定对此光源采集的 light samples（灯光采样）数量覆盖值。如果设置为非零值，它会覆盖 Integrator 执行的采样。如果此灯光存在难以解决的噪声并需要更多采样，你可能会需要此设置。"}
{"id":"2d8fba8ebbdac809a6b4dc990dad84d2cab9902dda48ebf9033d51c80f3f762e","item_id":"6b5d66625e:116","text":"Light Group"}
{"id":"cde9225a0ed6e632073bdbbf1b623c2d93b694742d25d19261db39bf12b9c88a","item_id":"6b5d66625e:117","text":"指定用于 light group LPEs 的灯光组名称。这有助于生成 per-light AOVs（逐灯光 AOV），以便之后在合成中调整。"}
{"id":"69ae9f2080b40b43d5835993c632d37f17f0c11a9e82f03fb3ccd8917d41d6d1","item_id":"6b5d66625e:118","text":"Importance Multiplier（重要性倍增）"}
{"id":"9b5c2200782f28fd52acb99cf96be1dffc06ae3a29f939a686305bd9a3aefc2c","item_id":"6b5d66625e:119","text":"与显式设置 Light Samples 不同，用户可以通过更改此值来改变灯光在内部被分配到的采样数量。RenderMan 会在渲染时为场景中的所有灯光创建一组采样，更改此值会在各灯光之间重新平衡采样。注意，增加此值会使"}
{"id":"187897ce0afcf20b50ba2b37dca84a951b7046f29ed5ab94f010619f69d6e189","item_id":"6b5d66625e:120","text":"更多"}
{"id":"cc24e9cc8cb656788d9f07b858341db5c3254e71c26420b4c86ff31f1f5dfd94","item_id":"6b5d66625e:121","text":"采样从该灯光中选择，同时减少场景中其他灯光的采样。低于默认值则会"}
{"id":"b2dc971f4895ca1f298f3f72fa80f67a6a2100532dfc3e74898b93ab12fdb8cd","item_id":"6b5d66625e:122","text":"减少"}
{"id":"70ce2ded289575d403612cd4dc4c8326738b0d48ce47adbd0003fb715ce4b31d","item_id":"6b5d66625e:123","text":"该灯光的采样，并为场景中其他灯光提供更多采样。"}
{"id":"954f93fe1c66ae447f4d9e75eb0dc5a32f3a45dfc1cfb6df391a9d5947a97d10","item_id":"6b5d66625e:124","text":"Presets（预设）"}
{"id":"49b25b4d32a644f8ad090ec15c5054e1018d0bd66304b7d04962be31ad53f668","item_id":"6b5d66625e:125","text":"RenderMan for Maya 包含针对一天中特定时间的实用预设。"}
